    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, then chop them finely and discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add most<strong> </strong>of the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the cooked bulgur wheat and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby bulgur</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1717402238535-x200.jpg",
